00:06:16,519 --> 00:06:18,160
"'and that He was buried, and that He rose again

151
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:21,459
"'the third day, according to the scriptures,

152
00:06:21,459 --> 00:06:24,500
"'and that He was seen of Cephas, then of the twelve.

153
00:06:24,500 --> 00:06:28,559
"'After that, He was seen of above 500 brethren at once,

