00:06:46,440 --> 00:06:47,640
As we look at this passage of scripture this morning,

161
00:06:47,640 --> 00:06:49,640
we're reminded that Paul was speaking

162
00:06:49,640 --> 00:06:52,880
about the certainty, the reality of Christ's resurrection.

163
00:06:52,880 --> 00:06:54,619
