251
00:10:46,279 --> 00:10:48,839
There's not a just man upon the face of the earth.

252
00:10:48,839 --> 00:10:54,239
The only one to ever walk the face of this earth without sin is Jesus Christ himself,

253
00:10:54,239 --> 00:10:56,059
God in flesh.

254
00:10:56,059 --> 00:10:58,519
And so sin is a universal condition.

255
00:10:58,519 --> 00:11:03,519
Every single one of us, we sang that song this morning about the, it's under the blood.

256
00:11:03,519 --> 00:11:09,199
And the reality is that I'm so thankful this morning that I can say that yes, I'm a sinner,

